---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Noisedrops"
  description="What is Noisedrops? A calm, minimal ambient sound library built for focus, rest, and being present."
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8">About Noisedrops</h1>

        <div class="prose-like space-y-6 text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Noisedrops is an ambient sound library built for people who need a room, not a song.
            Long videos. Real environments. No narration.
          </p>

          <p>
            Every upload is a place — a laundromat at 11pm, a train moving through rain, a coffee
            shop filling up slowly. You put it on, you get into your work, and the room does the
            rest.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink pt-4">Ambient Rooms</h2>
          <p>
            Each "room" on the site is a YouTube playlist — a category of similar soundscapes.
            Transit ambience. Rain. Cozy public spaces. New rooms get added as new environments
            are recorded.
          </p>
          <p>
            Only long-form videos appear here. No Shorts. Nothing under a minute. If it's here, it
            was made to be played for a while.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink pt-4">The Channel</h2>
          <p>
            All content lives on YouTube. This site is the quiet front door — a calmer way to
            browse and find what you need.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@noisedrops"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block bg-accent text-white text-sm font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-accent/80 transition-colors text-center"
          >
            Visit the Channel
          </a>
          <a
            href="/rooms"
            class="inline-block border border-surface-muted text-ink-muted text-sm font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:border-ink-faint hover:text-ink transition-colors text-center"
          >
            Browse Rooms
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
